      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="cache-aggressively-but-selectively"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Product titles and descriptions change rarely. Cache them for 1 to 24 hours. Inventory changes constantly. Never cache it for more than 60 seconds, and ideally pass through every read. Prices change in batches during promotions. Cache them with a short TTL and invalidate on webhook events.</p></div></div>
