    <div class="faq-a" id="why-this-step-matters-the-connector-layer-is-where"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Open <code>~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json</code> on macOS or <code>%APPDATA%\Claude\claude_desktop_config.json</code> on Windows. Add an entry for the catalog server.</p></div></div>
