    <div class="faq-a" id="customer-support-q-amp-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Customer asks "Does the merino crew sweater shrink in the wash?" The support agent (human or AI) calls the catalog server, pulls the care instructions metafield, and answers with the actual product data. Resolution time drops from 8 minutes to 90 seconds.</p></div></div>
