    <div class="faq-a" id="merchandising-assistance"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A merchandiser asks the assistant for products that are low on inventory but high on search demand. The agent joins the catalog server with the search analytics server, returns a ranked list, and proposes which to restock first. Decisions that took a Monday morning now happen in two minutes.</p></div></div>
