    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="internal-product-q-amp-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A new employee asks "Which of our sweaters are machine washable and cost under $80?" The assistant queries the catalog and returns three SKUs with the relevant attributes highlighted. Onboarding gets easier. Support handovers get faster.</p></div></div>
